  57,20,Know hoc worldly vita est non multus than play games ac boasting vos hoarding de moneta infans! It est abundant rain produces plants pleases disbelievers! Tunc plants turn into useless hay blown wind In Hereafter ibi est either severe retribution forgiveness ex DEUS approval Hoc worldly vita est non multus than temporary illusion
